OL,3,CStarmer has 'utterly failed' to help
OL,4,CScots during energy 'crisis', Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FWestminster has "failed" Scots on
OL,8,Fenergy policy, First Minister John
OL,9,FSwinney claimed, and the SNP leader
OL,10,Fsaid people were paying higher bills
OL,11,Fas a result of decisions made by UK
OL,12,Fministers.
OL,14,FMr Swinney accused the Labour
OL,15,FGovernment at Westminster of "standing
OL,16,Fby and doing nothing" in the midst of
OL,17,Fthe current energy crisis, during
OL,18,Fwhich action by the Gulf by the US and
OL,19,FIsrael, has caused oil and gas prices
OL,20,Fto surge.
OL,26,@oD@QOUoD@XO]wD@^OUxD@UO]
