OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775502670
OL,3,CStarmer has 'utterly failed' to help
OL,4,CScots during energy 'crisis', Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FHe said Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer had "utterly failed in his
OL,9,Fresponsibilities during a time of
OL,10,Fnational crisis".
OL,12,FMr Swinney described Scotland as an
OL,13,F"energy superpower", with both
OL,14,Frenewable energy resources and North
OL,15,FSea oil and gas, but blamed
OL,16,Fpoliticians in London for the "soaring
OL,17,Fcosts" of fuel.
OL,26,@pD@MOUrD@PO]uD@AOUuD@SO]xD@_OUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
