FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775502670
OL,3,CStarmer has 'utterly failed' to help
OL,4,CScots during energy 'crisis', Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FBut he said bills could be cut with
OL,8,Fthe "fresh start of independence",
OL,9,Fwhich would mean Scotland taking
OL,10,Fcharge of energy policy instead of it
OL,11,Fbeing reserved to Westminster.
OL,13,FHe was speaking as he prepared to
OL,14,Fvisit a renewable energy project in
OL,15,FEastwood, outside Glasgow, in the run
OL,16,Fup to the Scottish Parliament election
OL,17,Fon May 7.
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
