PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775502670
OL,3,CStarmer has 'utterly failed' to help
OL,4,CScots during energy 'crisis', Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMr Swinney said: "Scotland is an
OL,8,Fenergy superpower. Whether through the
OL,9,FNorth Sea or our extraordinary clean,
OL,10,Frenewable energy resources, we produce
OL,11,Fmore energy than we need.
OL,13,F"Yet we pay higher bills than we
OL,14,Fshould thanks to decisions taken in
OL,15,FWestminster.
OL,17,F"It is frankly outrageous that
OL,18,FScotland is one of the most energy-
OL,19,Frich countries in the world and yet we
OL,20,Fpay some of the highest energy prices.
OL,26,@oD@ROUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
