OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775502670
OL,3,CStarmer has 'utterly failed' to help
OL,4,CScots during energy 'crisis', Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"People are struggling to heat their
OL,8,Fhomes and facing soaring costs at the
OL,9,Fpetrol pumps in a nation with abundant
OL,10,Fresources. That demonstrates just how
OL,11,Fbadly Westminster has failed."
OL,13,FSpeaking about the current "energy
OL,14,Fcrisis" he said that "people in
OL,15,FScotland are looking for help with sky-
OL,16,Fhigh bills and petrol prices".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@^O]uD@\OUvD@GO]vD@VOUxD@]O]
