OL,3,CStarmer has 'utterly failed' to help
OL,4,CScots during energy 'crisis', Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FBut he claimed: "The UK Labour
OL,8,FGovernment is standing by and doing
OL,9,Fnothing. This is a Labour Prime
OL,10,FMinister that has utterly failed in
OL,11,Fhis responsibilities during a time of
OL,12,Fnational crisis.
OL,14,F"So let me be clear ` if Westminster
OL,15,Fwill not act to bring bills down, they
OL,16,Fshould get out of the road and hand
OL,17,Fthe powers to an SNP government that
OL,18,Fwill."
OL,26,@oD@QOUvD@AOUzD@FO]
