OL,3,CStarmer has 'utterly failed' to help
OL,4,CScots during energy 'crisis', Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FHe added that "for decades" the UK
OL,8,FGovernment had "squandered" North Sea
OL,9,Frevenues, adding: "We cannot afford to
OL,10,Flet them do the same to our vast
OL,11,Frenewable energy wealth.
OL,13,F"Scotland's energy must work for
OL,14,FScotland's people ` and when
OL,15,FWestminster takes the decisions,
OL,16,FWestminster takes the wealth.
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@[O]pD@POUpD@[O]qD@SOUuD@AOU
