PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775502670
OL,3,CStarmer has 'utterly failed' to help
OL,4,CScots during energy 'crisis', Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"With the fresh start of independence
OL,8,Fputting control over Scotland's energy
OL,9,Fin Scotland's hands, we can make our
OL,10,Fenergy wealth work for Scotland and
OL,11,Fbring down bills."
OL,13,FGregor Poynton, Labour MP for
OL,14,FLivingston said: "After nearly two
OL,15,Fdecades of broken promises and bungled
OL,16,Fplans, no one believes a word John
OL,17,FSwinney and the SNP have to say.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@RO]vD@ROU
