PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775502670
OL,3,CStarmer has 'utterly failed' to help
OL,4,CScots during energy 'crisis', Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"The SNP sold off Scotland's seabeds
OL,8,Fon the cheap, blocked investment in
OL,9,Fclean nuclear power and piled pressure
OL,10,Fon working Scots with tax hikes and
OL,11,Funaffordable housing costs.
OL,13,F"This tired and complacent SNP
OL,14,Fgovernment has no real answers to the
OL,15,Fchallenges Scotland faces.
OL,17,F"The only way to deliver change for
OL,18,FScotland and make life more affordable
OL,19,Fis by voting Scottish Labour on May 7."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU{D@gO]
