OL,3,CStarmer has 'utterly failed' to help
OL,4,CScots during energy 'crisis', Swinney
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FA UK Government spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Families and businesses will be
OL,9,Fworried about the impact of conflict
OL,10,Fin the Middle East here at home.
OL,12,F"The government is determined to fight
OL,13,Fpeople's corner.
OL,15,F"Our clean energy superpower mission
OL,16,Fis the route to energy sovereignty,
OL,17,Flower bills and thousands of good jobs
OL,18,Fin our communities."
